title: DEID builds a suspended footbridge in Japo, Bolivia in 2022.

media:group.media:title: DEID builds a suspended footbridge in Japo, Bolivia in 2022.
media:group.media:description:
Student members of Duke Engineers for International Development traveled to Japo, Bolivia in the summer of 2022 to help construct a footbridge across a gorge that was impassible during seasonal rains.  Watch the video to learn how the students built so much more!

Learn all about their experience at https://pratt.duke.edu/about/news/deid-returns-new-bridge-bolivia
